{"tid":769835,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀ou 既同學提提你","createTime":"2018-08-06T13:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T16:59:05.000Z","uid":137190,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdaa4f6af4ca5ebeeda2e45fec6ea4047ab5a37","tid":769835,"uid":137190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"如果你main round 派到ou 既果段reject offer 信我 入完你一定後悔四年 <br />\n1.圖書館細基本上每科都係得幾本參考書比你借 課外書直頭一本都冇 簡單講圖書館規模仲差過我屋企樓下屋村圖書館<br />\n2. 學費唔穩定隨時加 我記得上年學費扣左$30000 overall 係交3-4 萬 但下個sem 1 學費 加到2 萬幾 姐全年差唔多4 萬記 。 <br />\n3. 好少機會去到外國exchange 我睇咁耐email 5 個同外國有關既都唔知有冇 相反去大陸exchange 既就大把<br />\n4.有極多伏科去拖抵你成績 特別係冇固定答案果D 點比分真係任佢up （佢唔會公開marking)所以gpa 冇咩可能爆到4 trans u <br />\n5. retake 學費貴到仆街 成7-8000 一科 食水深到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6.學校福利極少 唔似其他u 咁可以$10-20 睇醫生 洗牙<br />\n7. 上網都見到既 campus 細 冇u life 我就唔講<br />\n<br />\n如果派到ou 就果斷入hkcc ！ 2 年後一條好漢 。  hkcc 既野真係易到仆街 見過佢其實一科既notes 成份得10 幾頁 每頁得一至兩行英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b453234b5b50d1571e69445cf26a86e6fb24cda5","tid":769835,"uid":136759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"真 去過一次都唔會想讀 細過隔離間小學 真係搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dd6039cea3d6a5e2e19d468e7aa8e8338d3428","tid":769835,"uid":137190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"Push !"},{"pid":"c4a45a625d59e8e6ccbd2fc74ba4dc39a6eefa90","tid":769835,"uid":137190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"千其唔好比身邊既人左右 你既選擇 千其唔好為degree 而為OU 過來人話你知一定會後悔"},{"pid":"11decaaf3282a0ef1fcc31e6defb7a32fa628603","tid":769835,"uid":136759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T23:13:44.000Z","msg":"腳踏實地好過"},{"pid":"6dd74dd9f3a3e99d87ed0f1103127a0ffe17fb6a","tid":769835,"uid":166815,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"11decaaf3282a0ef1fcc31e6defb7a32fa628603","tid":769835,"uid":136759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T23:13:44.000Z","msg":"腳踏實地好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"同意，真係唔好為叫所謂學士而讀<br />\n<br />\n見倒飛箭OU五毛係好多個post搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/764021/page/8\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/764021/page/8</a><br />\n<br />\n等我入黎講兩句<br />\n<br />\nOU同正常大學唔同級<br />\n<br />\n垃圾OU仔俾2018 DSE考生的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/621552/page/3\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/621552/page/3</a><br />\n<br />\n#66 飛箭: <br />\n<br />\n香港十間大學為名的學校，只有三大：港、中、科 係真正既大學。理、城 都只係有大學名既進階版IVE。浸會宜家重有好多人看作次等大學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於嶺南、教院、樹仁、OU都係空有大學之名，並無大學之實。四間DSE收分最多的科都只係20幾分，教院成日買廣告的自資、同埋樹仁、OU，收唔少連十七、八分都無，政府比黎四間升呢用大學名，係對大學之名的侮辱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦，根本你想拉低其他U等佢地望落同OU一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自己軟弱想掩飾OU的不足<br />\n<br />\n我再講一次，OU同八大係唔同級，定位都唔同，但自由度都唔同，所以產出的(人)目標都唔同(雖然不排除有的人可以再突破)<br />\n<br />\n同埋你上面話有OU仔囉金馬獎所以唔廢根本係無力的<br />\n<br />\n第一唔係個個讀動漫都囉金馬獎<br />\n<br />\n其二呢的單一課業為本的評轄根本唔知學生參與左幾多，隨時可以係老師代做(有錯請指正)<br />\n<br />\nOU仔玻璃心: 見倒老師話畢業展質素一般甚至去到差，仲要無一有驚喜，就拎金馬獎頂<br />\n<br />\n下面個post見倒你筆跡，重唔係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/479867/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/479867/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/220419_ad2349012abf4e24c1fd73ddb5d8fbae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F220419_ad2349012abf4e24c1fd73ddb5d8fbae.jpg&h=3c1cd2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPolyU 藝術與設計係QS 大學排名全球第24位，而OU係勿都無<br />\n<br />\nOverall Score: 75.6<br />\nAcademic Reputation: 75.4<br />\nEmployer Reputation: 77.3<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.topuniversities.com/universities/hong-kong-polytechnic-university\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.topuniversities.com%2Funiversities%2Fhong-kong-polytechnic-university&d=bt6mqRAg2YYeN8gMcVdIBrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=61e22b25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.topuniversities.com/universities/hong-kong-polytechnic-university</a><br />\n<br />\n只係計僱主同學術聲譽，咪屈人排名只係靠出paper刷<br />\n<br />\n唔同就係唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOU就係OU，比人年滿17歲成本低的甘去讀咪算囉"},{"pid":"d8cc4048759d0c935538f9ba2778b68108073b98","tid":769835,"uid":71748,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"OU 本來就應該淨係比社會人讀<br />\n都唔知邊年開始收中學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39985d4726df7049deee247fdee93756f58ad638","tid":769835,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"oU 我地d 兼讀制租locker $100半年 何文田 得150個位要抽，畢業要俾畢業費才畢到業"}]}